{"lemma":"عَرَبِيَّةٍ","slug":"عَرَبِيَّةٍ","root":"ع.ر.ب","root_slug":"ع-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ب","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَرَبِيّ","root":"عرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28544"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"alternative spelling of عَرَبِيّ (ʕarabiyy) (Nile Valley, traditional spelling)","tags":["alt-of","alternative","masculine"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"alternative spelling of عَرَبِيّ (ʕarabiyy) (Nile Valley, traditional spelling)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28544","headword_ar":"عَرَبِىٌّ","root":"Erb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEarabu AlEarabiy~apu","text_ar":"العَرَبُ العَرَبِيَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEarabu","text_ar":"العَرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first quarter. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tanoqu$uwA fiY xawaAtiymikumo Earabiy~FA","text_ar":"لَا تَنْقُشُوا فِى خَوَاتِيمِكُمْ عَرَبِيًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, O, K, TA,) in a trad., or, as some relate it, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEarabiy~apa","text_ar":"العَرَبِيَّةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Engrave not on your signets"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muHam~adN","text_ar":"مُحَمَّدٌ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasuwlu A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"رَسُولُ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh, O, K, TA;) because this was engraved on the Prophet's own signet: (O, TA:) as though he had said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy~FA Earabiy~FA","text_ar":"نَبِيًّا عَرَبِيًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an Arabian prophet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning himself. (O, K, TA.) Omar said, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tanoqu$uwA fiY xawaAtiymikumu AlEarabiy~apa","text_ar":"لَا تَنْقُشُوا فِى خَوَاتِيمِكُمُ العَرَبِيَّةَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Engrave not on your signets Arabic"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and Ibn-'Omar disapproved of engraving on a signet words from the Kur-án. (Mgh, * O, TA.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarabiY~u Alwajohi","text_ar":"عَرَبِىُّ الوَجْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"often occurs in post-classical works as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having an Arab face;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"long-faced;"},{"kind":"text","text":"opposed to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"turokiY~u","text_ar":"تُرْكِىُّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwajohi","text_ar":"الوَجْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraAbN","text_ar":"عِرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places.       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A white barley, the ears of which are bifurcate"},{"kind":"text","text":"[so I render, agreeably with the TK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sunobuluhu","text_ar":"سُنْبُلُهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HarofaAni","text_ar":"حَرْفَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is wide, and its grain is large, larger than the grain of the barley of El- 'Irak, and it is the best of barley."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","O","K","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}